                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-320</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After the EAR is redeployed the JPAAppender stops logging.&lt;br/&gt;
